title: Pepperoni Bread
ingredients: ["1 loaf frozen bread", "1 egg, beaten", "1 1/2 c. shredded Mozzarella cheese", "1 1/2 c. pepperoni", "1 Tbsp. butter"]
directions: ["Let bread thaw and rise, as per the package instructions. Roll as flat as possible.", "Top with butter, cheese and pepperoni. Roll up like a jelly roll.", "Spread egg over top and seal.", "Bake on foiled cookie sheet at 350\u00b0 for 25 minutes."]
